crmrte: Medium negative correlation with prbarr and prbconv. Low positive correlation with prbpris prbarr: Low correlation with prbconv and prbpris. prbconv: Low correlation with prbpris. prbpris: Low correlation with all.

Single Variable Conclusion: crmrte and prbpris have the most normal distribution of the four variables. Note that those variable are not correlated with each other.
